staking.description: E loaʻa i ka loaʻa mālualua ma o ka kūpaʻa cryptocurrency me nā kumukūʻai APY paipai, nā manawa laka māʻalahi, a me ka hoʻomaʻemaʻe uku i hoʻonohonoho ʻia.

ico.title: Kūʻai Token
ico.description: E loaʻa koke i nā Hōʻike Kālā Mua i loiloi ʻia me nā hōʻike loiloi kūpono, ka loiloi tokenomics, a me ka nānā hoʻopuka waiwai.

marketplace.title: Mākeke
marketplace.description: E ʻimi i nā mākeke kikoʻī dijikala a kino me nā hoʻolimalima palekana, nā mea kūʻai i hōʻoia ʻia, a me ka mālama mea kūʻai paipai.

nft.title: Hale Kiʻi NFT
nft.description: E ʻike, e hana, a e kālepa i nā waihona kikohoʻe kūikawā ma kā mākou mākeke NFT i hoʻonohonoho ʻia me nā hiki kūʻai kālele a me nā uku loaʻa o nā mea hana.

store.title: Hale Kūʻai
store.description: Mākeke maikaʻi loa e hoʻolako ana i nā huahana kikohoʻe a me nā mea kino me ka hoʻoponopono uku palekana, ka hoʻouna honua, a me ka pale kūʻai.

services.title: Nā Lawelawe
services.description: Nā lawelawe ʻenehana a me nā mea hana e hoʻonui i kāu ʻike kālepa, e like me nā polokalamu hui, nā kumuwaiwai hoʻonaʻauao, a me ka kōkua maikaʻi.

affiliate.title: Polokalamu Hui
affiliate.description: E loaʻa ka dala ma o kou pūnaewele ma kā mākou polokalamu hui palapala me nā uku hui paʻa, ka nānā manawa maoli, a me nā mea hana hoʻolaha.

support.title: Kikowaena Kōkua
support.description: Kōkua mea kūʻai ʻenehana me ka hoʻokele tikeke, ka hiki kamaʻilio ola, a me ka hoʻokele moʻokāki kūikawā no nā mea hoʻohana maikaʻi.

faq.title: Waihona ʻIke
faq.description: Nā palapala palapala, nā aʻo, a me nā nīnau i nīnau pinepine ʻia e kōkua iā ʻoe e hoʻonui i nā hiki kahua.

insights.title: Nā Manaʻo Hohonu
insights.description: Ka loiloi mākeke ʻenehana, nā manaʻo kālepa, a me nā nūhou ʻoihana mai kā mākou hui loea kālā a me nā mea noiʻi mākeke.
